high_descs: Turn to the right and walk forward to face the counter.
pick up the knife on the counter.
Step to the left to face the apple on the counter.
Cut the apple into the pieces.
Look up to face the sink.
Place the knife in the right side of the sink
Look down to face the apple on the counter.
Pick up a piece of apple on the counter.
Turn to the left and face the microwave.
Heat the piece of apple in the microwave and then remove it.
Turn left and walk forward to face the counter.
Place the piece of apple on the counter.
anns.task_desc: To heat a piece of apple and place it on the counter.

high_descs: Turn to your right and go to the kitchen counter between the refrigerator and the sink.
Pick up the knife in front of the coffee maker and the toaster, on the counter.
Move over to your left so that you are in front of the sink.
Cut the apple, on the counter, in front of the sink, into slices.
Move forward, closer to the sink in front of you.
Place the knife in the center of the sink.
Move back, away from the sink.
Pick up one of the apple slices on the counter.
Turn to the microwave to your left.
Place the apple slice in the microwave, warm it, and then remove the apple slice from the microwave.
Turn to your left and walk to the counter across from you.
Place the apple slice on the counter, to the right of the green cup.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm apple slice on the counter.
